      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "<size=130%><b>GDPR & Privacy Notice</b></size>\r\n\r\n<size=85%>Last updated:
    March 2026</size>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>1. Who we are</b>  \r\nThis promotional activity
    is organized by <b>SANDAWOOL TRADING SRL</b>, the exclusive distributor of Agua
    de Madre products in Romania.  \r\n\r\nThe activity is conducted as part of the
    <b>COFFeEAST</b> event.  \r\n\r\nFor any questions regarding your personal data
    or this privacy notice, you can contact us at:  \r\n<b>Email:</b> aguademadre.ro@gmail.com 
    \r\n\r\n\r\n<b>2. What data we collect</b>  \r\nWhen you participate in the game,
    we may collect the following personal data:  \r\n\u2022 Full name  \r\n\u2022
    Email address  \r\n\u2022 Phone number  \r\n\r\n\r\n<b>3. Why we collect your
    data</b>  \r\nWe collect and use your data for the following purposes:  \r\n\r\n\u2022
    <b>Contest administration</b> \u2013 to contact you if you win a prize  \r\n\u2022
    <b>Communication</b> \u2013 to send you updates, offers, and promotions related
    to our drinks business  \r\n\r\n\r\n<b>4. Legal basis (GDPR)</b>  \r\nWe process
    your data based on:  \r\n\u2022 <b>Your consent</b> (by ticking \"I Accept GDPR\") 
    \r\n\r\nYou have the right to withdraw your consent at any time.  \r\n\r\n\r\n<b>5.
    How long we store your data</b>  \r\nWe will store your personal data only as
    long as necessary:  \r\n\u2022 For contest purposes: until the winners are confirmed 
    \r\n\u2022 For marketing purposes: until you withdraw consent or request deletion 
    \r\n\r\n\r\n<b>6. Who we share your data with</b>  \r\nWe do <b>not sell your
    data</b>.  \r\n\r\nYour data may be processed by trusted service providers (e.g.,
    email or CRM tools) strictly for the purposes described above.  \r\n\r\n\r\n<b>7.
    Your rights</b>  \r\nUnder GDPR, you have the following rights:  \r\n\u2022 Access
    your data  \r\n\u2022 Correct your data  \r\n\u2022 Request deletion (\"right
    to be forgotten\")  \r\n\u2022 Restrict or object to processing  \r\n\u2022 Data
    portability  \r\n\r\nTo exercise any of these rights, contact us at:  \r\n<b>aguademadre.ro@gmail.com</b> 
    \r\n\r\n\r\n<b>8. Data security</b>  \r\nWe take appropriate technical and organizational
    measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, loss, or misuse. 
    \r\n\r\n\r\n<b>9. Withdrawal of consent</b>  \r\nYou can withdraw your consent
    at any time by contacting us.  \r\n\r\nThis will not affect the legality of processing
    before withdrawal.  \r\n\r\n\r\n<b>10. Complaints</b>  \r\nIf you believe your
    data is not handled properly, you have the right to lodge a complaint with: 
    \r\n\r\n<b>ANSPDCP</b> (Romanian Data Protection Authority)  \r\n\r\n\r\n<size=115%><b>Consent</b></size> 
    \r\nBy ticking <b>\"I Accept GDPR\"</b>, you confirm that:  \r\n\r\n\u2022 You
    have read and understood this notice  \r\n\u2022 You agree to the collection
    and use of your data as described above  "
